Functional Components:
Nothing but js functions. They are independent, and they will not have any knowledge on
what is going to happen in other component.

Syntax:
function MyFunction() {
return (
    <h1>Hii</h1>
);
}


Class Component:
Class component are complex by nanture. Class components can work with each other.

Syntax:

class MyClassComponent extends React.Component {
     render() {
        return <h1>Hello you!!</h1>
     }
}
